#螢幕上繪圖-turtle
`
import turtle

turtle . pensize(4)
turtle . pencolor('red')
turtle . forward ( 100 )
turtle . right ( 90 )
turtle . forward ( 100 )
turtle . right ( 90 )
turtle . forward ( 100 )
turtle . right ( 90 )
turtle . forward ( 100 )
turtle . mainloop ()
`
可以劃出一個紅色正方型。
